snippet.title: The Sims 3 Late Night Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Discover life after dark in The Sims™ 3 Late Night Expansion Pack! Wherever your Sims go, they'll discover new things to become—adored celebrities, all-night partiers, rowdy bandmates, or alluring vampires. What will your Sims get up to after dark?
